main event: A reported UFO sighting involving two circular objects flying at a high altitude without sound.
interesting points: The objects were approximately arm's length and no tail contrails were observed., The sighting occurred between 6 to 20 degrees above the horizon., The objects followed a straight path overhead., The sighting was confirmed by tower personnel at Walker AFB, New Mexico., No physical evidence of the sighting was recorded.
witness description: The report mentions confirmation by tower personnel but does not specify individual witnesses.
